pf.graph
Class VertexImpl

java.lang.Object
  pf.graph.VertexImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<Edge>, Graph, Vertex
public class VertexImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements Vertex

Default implementation of Vertex.

It has two independent maps of edges. One for all edges, the other one for unused edges only.

Many methods defined in Graph are unsupported in context of vertex. They just throw an UnsupportedOperationException. Others have a trivial implementation.

Author:
Adam Juraszek
